Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [01/12/2024]  
[AnandJMS] ("we," "our," or "us") operates [AnandJMS], available on the Google Play Store. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app.  

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:  

a. Personal Information
- Name, email address, and other details you provide when creating an account or contacting us.  

b. Non-Personal Information
- Usage data, device information, and analytics for improving app performance.  

2. How We Use Your Information 
We use the collected data to:  
- Provide and maintain the app's functionality.  
- Improve app features and user experience.  
- Send important updates and notifications.  
- Ensure security and prevent misuse.  

3. Third-Party Services
Our app uses third-party services, such as Firebase, for analytics, authentication, and other functionalities. These services may collect data as described in their privacy policies:  
- [Google Firebase Privacy Policy](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)  

4. Data Security
We are committed to protecting your data. While no system is completely secure, we implement reasonable measures to safeguard your information from unauthorized access or misuse.  

5. Your Rights
You have the right to:  
- Access the data we hold about you.  
- Request correction or deletion of your data.  
- Opt-out of certain data collection activities.  

